{"tid":1735963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警係咁散播二噁英 算唔算違反《禁止化學武器公約》","createTime":"2019-11-18T16:15:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T01:59:47.000Z","uid":134111,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"dcff6905acad858b080ca403f882cc631cac7247","tid":1735963,"uid":134111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:15:43.000Z","msg":"而家黑警全面用哂大陸啲TG 比人發現到會放出大量二噁英 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尋日理大有人測山埃含量 結果爆埋錶<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZN8ddAt.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZN8ddAt.gif&h=45ec30e9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n結果我去check下wiki 發現二噁英俗稱為「戴奧辛」（dioxins）毒性與沙林相近<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UFD8M6p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUFD8M6p.png&h=ad10d54e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而沙林正正就係一種神經性毒劑既生化武器 咁理論上二噁英都應該會係差唔多既野<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MtuPwyj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMtuPwyj.png&h=69c451a2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n國際之間就曾經簽訂《禁止化學武器公約》 而中國都有簽定:<br />\nKey points of the Convention<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1.<span style=\"color: red;\">Prohibition of production and use of chemical weapons</span></span><br />\n2.Destruction (or monitored conversion to other functions) of chemical weapons production facilities<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3<span style=\"color: red;\">.Destruction of all chemical weapons (including chemical weapons abandoned outside the state parties territory)</span></span><br />\n4.Assistance between State Parties and the OPCW in the case of use of chemical weapons<br />\n5.An OPCW inspection regime for the production of chemicals which might be converted to chemical weapons<br />\n6. International cooperation in the <span style=\"color: red;\">peaceful use</span> of chemistry in relevant areas<br />\n<br />\n化學武器物質分類<br />\n《禁止化學武器公約》規定受控制的化學武器物質分為三類。[24] 分類依據是可以合法製造、民用的數量。 每一類分為可直接作為化學武器的「部分A」與作為製造化學武器的原料的「部分B」。<br />\n一類物質：化學武器以外的用途極少。可以用於研究、醫療、製藥、化學武器防禦測試等目的。每年製造100克以上就必須向OPCW登記. 一個國家被限於最多擁有1噸這些物質。例如，芥子氣與神經毒劑.<br />\n二類物質：有合法的小規模民用。此類物質的製造必須登記，禁止出口給非公約簽署國。例如，硫二甘醇用於製造芥子氣，也用來作為墨水的溶劑。<br />\n三類物質：有合法的大規模民用。年產30噸以上的工廠必須登記，允許檢查。限制出口給非公約簽署國。例如，光氣, 可以直接作為化學武器，也是許多合法的有機化合物製造的前體；三乙醇胺用於製造芥子氣，也用於製造化妝品及洗滌劑。<br />\n<br />\n催淚彈作為事裝備 我諗都無咩可能係合法民用 所以應該係第一類物質<br />\n咁問題係而家港共政府透過催淚和驅散人群為名 黎散播二噁英<br />\n警政府公開認左催淚彈會放二噁英都堅持使用 令香港變成了一個毒城 再係咁落去真係可能滅族<br />\n呢啲生物武器理應要燒毀 但家警政府唔單單持有生物武器 仲用埋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我想問下咁算唔算違反《禁止化學武器公約》?<br />\n如果唔算的話 大家可以係國際公約果方面搵搵料 等國際多樣理由幫香港<br />\n如果算違反的話 希望大家可以向國際求救 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為化學武器香港人真係搞唔掂 連個政府都唔識搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申: 本人對化學了解唔多, 法律近乎零知識 <br />\n以上資料全部都可以係wiki搵到<br />\n key words:二噁英,禁止生物武器公約(Chemical Weapons Convention),化學武器<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73c1e23c4da385c657b5f2a1e7b263a612ed0776","tid":1735963,"uid":235909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:27:38.000Z","msg":"多謝資料，我都唔係化學人，但我可以我試下搵搵<br />\n簡單搵左少少，當年越南有告過美國，但唔成功，可能冇案例。<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/amphtml/閻紀宇專欄-在熱帶叢林灑下世紀之毒-返鄉才發現噩夢-路跟隨-從紀錄片-224001786.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2Famphtml%2F%E9%96%BB%E7%B4%80%E5%AE%87%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E5%9C%A8%E7%86%B1%E5%B8%B6%E5%8F%A2%E6%9E%97%E7%81%91%E4%B8%8B%E4%B8%96%E7%B4%80%E4%B9%8B%E6%AF%92-%E8%BF%94%E9%84%89%E6%89%8D%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E5%99%A9%E5%A4%A2-%E8%B7%AF%E8%B7%9F%E9%9A%A8-%E5%BE%9E%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84%E7%89%87-224001786.htm&d=rVb%2FtPUztGFmJk27tPFGPuQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=69cd8ed6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/amphtml/閻紀宇專欄-在熱帶叢林灑下世紀之毒-返鄉才發現噩夢-路跟隨-從紀錄片-224001786.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n但如果證實到凡係有目的地散播對人體有害既野，能唔能夠入到罪，就要搵法律既朋友幫手，我都知好多有心律師都幫緊手足......但唔知有冇啲可以幫手比啲意見？"},{"pid":"77ac3cd7ba49f9bc2820715400365c61b66715cf","tid":1735963,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:28:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9678ee36db489ec4243ace08a7d0af29691aec27","tid":1735963,"uid":5662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:29:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"15e42f24629d42bbcc3cc88f6de7e9fe9197aeb5","tid":1735963,"uid":127418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:30:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bc4d6ceb76aba38da5754ab23bdd5a023e1750c0","tid":1735963,"uid":134111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:34:14.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6648f77cd016fdf16e6153ff11eaf2871bacb387","tid":1735963,"uid":235909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:47:33.000Z","msg":"我驚我唔記得，我搵到既貼，大家幫手睇睇<br />\n有個美國左翼既新聞網： CounterPunch <br />\n係2015 post左篇文：<br />\n40 years on the Vietnam War continues for victims of agent orange<br />\n<br />\n文中其中一句指出The use of Agent Orange in Vietnam constituted prohibited chemical warfare, amounting to a war crime. <br />\n<br />\n<strong>使用橙劑為戰爭罪行</strong><br />\n<br />\n橙劑中含有Dioxin <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.counterpunch.org/2015/12/17/40-years-on-the-vietnam-war-continues-for-victims-of-agent-orange/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.counterpunch.org%2F2015%2F12%2F17%2F40-years-on-the-vietnam-war-continues-for-victims-of-agent-orange%2F&d=rVb%2FtPUztGFmJk27tPFGPuQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=9b78808e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.counterpunch.org/2015/12/17/40-years-on-the-vietnam-war-continues-for-victims-of-agent-orange/</