pid":"85ac5e292761523f8834350875c3bd5eff0a0682","tid":1735963,"uid":134111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:00:00.000Z","msg":"跪求手足們係呢方面做多啲野<br />\n打通呢條國際戰線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nHong Kong really need your help<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c05b925074e14446f52d8b24b29efaa078c46dcf","tid":1735963,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"284a1711766a1983d38afa1a48666ced6758c3ac","tid":1735963,"uid":134111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6648f77cd016fdf16e6153ff11eaf2871bacb387","tid":1735963,"uid":235909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:47:33.000Z","msg":"我驚我唔記得，我搵到既貼，大家幫手睇睇<br />\n有個美國左翼既新聞網： CounterPunch <br />\n係2015 post左篇文：<br />\n40 years on the Vietnam War continues for victims of agent orange<br />\n<br />\n文中其中一句指出The use of Agent Orange in Vietnam constituted prohibited chemical warfare, amounting to a war crime. <br />\n<br />\n<strong>使用橙劑為戰爭罪行</strong><br />\n<br />\n橙劑中含有Dioxin <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.counterpunch.org/2015/12/17/40-years-on-the-vietnam-war-continues-for-victims-of-agent-orange/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.counterpunch.org%2F2015%2F12%2F17%2F40-years-on-the-vietnam-war-continues-for-victims-of-agent-orange%2F&d=rVb%2FtPUztGFmJk27tPFGPuQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=9b78808e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.counterpunch.org/2015/12/17/40-years-on-the-vietnam-war-continues-for-victims-of-agent-orange/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:57:49.000Z","msg":"如果係告到既話 而家就應該拎啲催淚彈sample比外國化驗所<br />\n證明而家啲催淚彈會放二噁英<br />\n再告班popo 上國際法庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果使用橙劑為戰爭罪行 使用二噁英都應該係戰爭罪行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:00:56.