s/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:00:56.000Z","msg":"應該向邊度告"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:13:27.000Z","msg":"International Court of Justice 國際法庭<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.icj-cij.org/en/how-the-court-works\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icj-cij.org%2Fen%2Fhow-the-court-works&d=rVb%2FtPUztGFmJk27tPFGPuQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=5d9ccc4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.icj-cij.org/en/how-the-court-works</a>"},{"pid":"1741f88ce28580466b9ada4a3234a8f739e99709","tid":1735963,"uid":235909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:14:30.000Z","msg":"有冇識法律既朋友？ 幫手睇睇上國際法庭既提告點做？"},{"pid":"191abeaa2451110c3c2d748d2e8f95db37f25401","tid":1735963,"uid":134111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:16:28.000Z","msg":"需要法律朋友既協助 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dbce1906f80e1f03e4150926de7d4297d9dd9c5","tid":1735963,"uid":46271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:17:08.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"0c083fdf6173375acc38a099ad21ace61276f4d3","tid":1735963,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:18:04.000Z","msg":"ｐｕｓｈ！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"02ebc9f0582187536e5740a4c70c5ec67801c803","tid":1735963,"uid":199845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:18:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"689bb3af863276b7fcea2cb73de76b7336620175","tid":1735963,"uid":124252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:18:55.000Z","msg":"違反又點？違反左好多野啦"},{"pid":"111d4377fb2bc010a821a0dc7bb2e3943adfeedb","tid":1735963,"uid":175346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:20:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3418c17757fbc28d957e2109be59e69a12b0e357","tid":1735963,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:21:44.000Z","msg":"係又點 外國完全WFC我地呀依家"},{"pid":"cdaf57fea0eb81cb40f78c375ef2dcb4e18a3161","tid":1735963,"uid":29302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:22:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1457e578d6c4871a8da9cb46ebd8dc8436df345f","tid":1735963,"uid":187112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcff6905acad858b080ca403f882cc631cac7247","tid":1735963,"uid":134111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:15:43.000Z","msg":"而家黑警全面用哂大陸啲TG 比人發現到會放出大量二噁英 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尋日理大有人測山埃含量 結果爆埋錶<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZN8ddAt.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZN8ddAt.gif&h=45ec30e9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n結果我去check下wiki 發現二噁英俗稱為「戴奧辛」（dioxins）毒性與沙林相近<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UFD8M6p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUFD8M6p.png&h=ad10d54e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而沙林正正就係一種神經性毒劑既生化武器 咁理論上二噁英都應該會係差唔多既野<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MtuPwyj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMtuPwyj.png&h=69c451a2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n國際之間就曾經簽訂《禁止化學武器公約》 而中國都有簽定:<br />\nKey points of the Convention<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1.<span style=\"color: red;\">Prohibition of production and use of chemical weapons</span></span><br />\n2.Destruction (or monitored conversion to other functions) of chemical weapons production facilities<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3<span style=\"color: red;\">.Destruction of all chemical weapons (including chemical weapons abandoned outside the state parties territory)</span></span><br />\n4.Assistance between State Parties and the OPCW in the case of use of chemical weapons<br />\n5.An OPCW inspection regime for the production of chemicals which might be converted to chemical weapons<br />\n6. International cooperation in the <span style=\"color: red;\">peaceful use</span> of chemistry in relevant areas<br />\n<br />\n化學武器物質分類<br />\n《禁止化學武器公約》規定受控制的化學武器物質分為三類。[24] 分類依據是可以合法製造、民用的數量。 每一類分為可直接作為化學武器的「部分A」與作為製造化學武器的原料的「部分B」。<br />\n一類物質：化學武器以外的用途極少。可以用於研究、醫療、製藥、化學武器防禦測試等目的。每年製造100克以上就必須向OPCW登記. 一個國家被限於最多擁有1噸這些物質。例如，芥子氣與神經毒劑.<br />\n二類物質：有合法的小規模民用。此類物質的製造必須登記，禁止出口給非公約簽署國。例如，硫二甘醇用於製造芥子氣，也用來作為墨水的溶劑。<br />\n三類物質：有合法的大規模民用。年產30噸以上的工廠必須登記，允許檢查。限制出口給非公約簽署國。例如，光氣, 可以直接作為化學武器，也是許多合法的有機化合物製造的前體；三乙醇胺用於製造芥子氣，也用於製造化妝品及洗滌劑。<br />\n<br />\n催淚彈作為事裝備 我諗都無咩可能係合法民用 所以應該係第一類物質<br />\n咁問題係而家港共政府透過催淚和驅散人群為名 黎散播二噁英<br />\n警政府公開認左催淚彈會放二噁英都堅持使用 令香港變成了一個毒城 再係咁落去真係可能滅族<br />\n呢啲生物武器理應要燒毀 但家警政府唔單單持有生物武器 仲用埋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我想問下咁算唔算違反《禁止化學武器公約》?<br />\n如果唔算的話 大家可以係國際公約果方面搵搵料 等國際多樣理由幫香港<br />\n如果算違反的話 希望大家可以向國際求救 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為化學武器香港人真係搞唔掂 連個政府都唔識搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申: 本人對化學了解唔多, 法律近乎零知識 <br />\n以上資料全部都可以係wiki搵到<br />\n key words:二噁英,禁止生物武器公約(Chemical Weapons Convention),化學武器<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:22:51.000Z","msg":"佢地會答你so what"},{"pid":"efa44986dab86fc86e2a4a7d9c3a10b0cd36d5c1","tid":1735963,"uid":134111,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"689bb3af863276b7fcea2cb73de76b7336620175","tid":1735963,"uid":124252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:18:55.000Z","msg":"違反又點？違反左好多野啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:23:26.000Z","msg":"popo/港共政府係違反左好多野 但唔代表我地要對呢不公義麻木<br />\n化學武器會毒害香港好幾代人 唔係就咁話係咁架啦 就可以算數<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f18f69a2e20ac9d2532b13d74755467899fb73e","tid":1735963,"uid":124252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efa44986dab86fc86e2a4a7d9c3a10b0cd36d5c1","tid":1735963,"uid":134111,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"689bb3af863276b7fcea2cb73d